rows.label: tlk43400046_04_msg0001
rows.name:
The Hræsvelgr Mercenaries... I'll say this,
they really know their trade.

rows.label: tlk43400046_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Dad's Viltsbine Mercs mainly operate
in Invidia...occasionally in Avaritia too.

rows.label: tlk43400046_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But the Hræsvelgr lot don't recognize
borders. They go wherever they're
needed.

rows.label: tlk43400046_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Not only that but they take on any
mission, no matter how tough or how
poorly rewarded.

rows.label: tlk43400046_04_msg0005
rows.name: All in all, they're just model mercs.

rows.label: tlk43400046_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Course...if they did it for nothing,
it'd be even more impressive.
